{"id":635313,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】公益时报中国殡葬周刊-河南省洛阳/","date":"2020-02-12T18:59:44Z","modified":"2020-02-12T19:55:12Z","title":"【立此存照】公益时报中国殡葬周刊 | 河南省洛阳殡仪馆党员突击队驰援武汉","content":"<p>CDT编者按：本文公众号原文已被删除</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2月7日，河南省洛阳殡仪馆举行了一场简短的“抗击疫情，驰援武汉，党员突击队”壮行仪式，三名支援武汉党员突击队员面对党旗宣誓，牢记初心使命，发挥党员的先锋模范作用，决不辜负领导的殷切期望，坚决完成党和人民交给的任务。</p>\n<p>据了解，这批支援武汉的党员突击队，是洛阳殡仪馆党支部根据专业和人员结构情况，精挑细选出的三名政治强、业务精、综合素质高的技术骨干组成，他们分别是王锐、宋林、张磊，主要任务支援武汉疫情防控工作。</p>\n<p>在当天举办的壮行仪式上，洛阳市民政局党组书记、局长巴永山向党员突击队授旗，他希望突击队员们，在抗击疫情的战斗中，要充分发挥党组织战斗堡垒和共产党员先锋模范作用，勇当抗击疫情的排头兵、急先锋，不负韶华、不辱使命，自觉肩负起“守土有责、守土尽责”的使命，用实际行动，交出一份让党和人民满意的答卷，尽心尽责完成组织上交给的任务，让党旗在疫情防控第一线高高飘扬。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635318\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/殡葬1-300x165.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/殡葬1-300x165.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/殡葬1.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>另外，重庆也有“援鄂殡葬服务队”到武汉支援：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635319\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0043-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0043-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0043-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0043.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635320\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0042-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0042-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0042-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/IMG_0042.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a>|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,39707],"tags":[39781,39648]}